EN: He arrived late due to a flight delay.

ZH: 抵达时，请注意行李安全。
EN: Please pay attention to luggage safety upon arrival.

ZH: 请随身携带重要物品，以防行李丢失抵达时遇到问题。
EN: Please carry important items with you in case there are issues with luggage loss upon arrival.

